{"tid":1385763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾健平獲准保釋 質疑警方專業","createTime":"2019-07-30T07:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T08:22:33.000Z","uid":28114,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"77c25e9d9b3fdb10469d1bb5e56f6dd401d287fd","tid":1385763,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"【鍾健平獲准保釋 質疑警方專業】<br />\n<br />\n日前申請元朗遊行被警方反對的市民鍾健平，前日被警方以涉嫌觸犯煽惑非法集結罪拘捕，同晚被押往其分別位於元朗及何文田的住所搜證並不得保釋。昨日早上鍾因背部傷患被送到大埔那打素醫院羈留病房留醫，直至是日中午獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n鍾的親友昨晚九時收到律師通知指鍾可以一千港元自簽保釋擔保，惟當親友帶同保釋金前往醫院時，警方重案組卻沒有解釋原因下拒絕保釋申請，相信是程序上的問題。警方於今早約十一時時許通知律師可以保釋，而鍾健平徵詢法律意見後接受保釋條件後獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n鍾現時神智清醒，仍然於那打素醫院留醫，接受本台訪問時表示於早上十一時收到警方的保釋條件，依然是與昨晚的保釋條件相同的一千港元自簽擔保。而鍾經諮詢法律意見後，即使只剩一小時就達四十八小時的情況下仍接受保釋條件，並需於八月二十九日下午三時到大埔警署報到。<br />\n<br />\n而在進行保釋程序期間，鍾發現載有他的私人財物，即應已密封的證物袋，被不知名人士曾經打開。證物袋內有他與律師的其他案件資料，包括並不限於元朗遊行之司法覆核的資料，而當日他與律師已表明他的私人財物包括手機及以上重要資料，但最後仍發現證物袋被打開，故考慮向廉政公署以公職人員行為失當的方向報案。<br />\n<br />\n對於今次的拘留，鍾表示不知道警察是否專業地處理他們認為是案件的案件，但質疑警察的手法是否香港人希望見到的所謂專業執法者。鍾先生亦指出如果他們是專業的執法者，他們應公正且不執行政治任務。<br />\n<br />\n鍾重申他當日並無參與遊行，而只是身為元朗土生土長的居民如常地在週末於元朗市逛街。對於各界關心其入院一事，鍾表示感謝並稱只是舊患復發，又表示於被捕後並沒有受到任何粗暴對待。<br />\n<br />\n鍾健平將於今晚八時半於那打素醫院地下會見傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n文:Jeffrey Cheng<br />\n#TMHK20190730<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Nba0ck.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Nba0ck.png&h=959233df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TMHK.ORG/photos/a.834946473239542/2358085860925588?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTMHK.ORG%2Fphotos%2Fa.834946473239542%2F2358085860925588%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI4aGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=4dccf292\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TMHK.ORG/photos/a.834946473239542/2358085860925588?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"ea7a6a2eb9f65a1c3b343f7bf156680bd30924c4","tid":1385763,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60126b26a2cf7ed20e56b3ffd37078b3f4326fde","tid":1385763,"uid":186961,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:13:58.000Z","msg":"煽惑非法集結罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬, 無人識佢㗎<br />\n個個入去食老婆餅又關姓鐘嘅咩事啊<br />\n你唔拉埋大同同恆香?"},{"pid":"103b70ba50a4e51a4e58dd5e939a3055347b8aa4","tid":1385763,"uid":214192,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"證物袋比人開好嚴重窩，特別係入面有其他案件嘅資料"},{"pid":"a49389ccb9bc1386be3b96c705abee9dbe0d92b1","tid":1385763,"uid":150427,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"103b70ba50a4e51a4e58dd5e939a3055347b8aa4","tid":1385763,"uid":214192,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"證物袋比人開好嚴重窩，特別係入面有其他案件嘅資料"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:21:22.000Z","msg":"(如果仲有公義) 上左庭, 因為開左證物袋, 律帥係可以幫佢打程序"},{"pid":"00eb32e8e91ff05b102dd9a27a5ad38d4c15ac72","tid":1385763,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:22:49.000Z","msg":"開左袋就狗狗煩死了"},{"pid":"465f3092a305c435502c43cba2bd4f88015117c7","tid":1385763,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:11:44.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96052bdbb8f6e6b1c5d32ab0642e6796df24de66","tid":1385763,"uid":277186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:13:24.000Z","msg":"呢個係咩人嚟㗎 唔識佢喎<br />\n佢一個人喺元朗行街點樣非法集結"},{"pid":"bf229ad47bf6cfb37cdfc988e20f05bba7dfbb2e","tid":1385763,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:14:27.000Z","msg":"佢真係慘<br />\n冇人識佢，冇拿拿比狗咬"},{"pid":"6c51f248e8562e221da8d7cc81dffa0df527592d","tid":1385763,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:15:24.000Z","msg":"根本入唔到佢罪"},{"pid":"345faeeed52f722bc118628eaf523912c9163a3e","tid":1385763,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:17:39.000Z","msg":"打開埋證件袋，仲有冇人可以制衡黑警權力"},{"pid":"fa65ecc0f16279a30c44e120bb992b38c80b9392","tid":1385763,"uid":12208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"345faeeed52f722bc118628eaf523912c9163a3e","tid":1385763,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:17:39.000Z","msg":"打開埋證件袋，仲有冇人可以制衡黑警權力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:18:56.000Z","msg":"共產黨<br />\n<br />\n依家既警察係黨衛兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a589c40cf48e806b104b9f7fba2bd16731e387c5","tid":1385763,"uid":64938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:19:10.000Z","msg":"[香城online]傳令兵的技巧和心得<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382782</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e96dc2d6792a127a57ab6a535001df58463ceaa0","tid":1385763,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:21:03.000Z","msg":"哇屌你老母一陣打開個證物袋塞包白粉入去我咪水洗都唔清?"},{"pid":"f3150af2b9d06e973b805f4a8605f4dad064bf7b","tid":1385763,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:22:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n自推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbGx8QX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfbGx8QX.jpg&h=d7da8d11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMXA6CM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMXA6CM.jpg&h=df77fed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jAzTbYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjAzTbYn.jpg&h=a3d7ff9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br /